\nabla \times (\nabla \times A) = \nabla (\nabla \cdot A) - (\nabla \cdot \nabla) A
e^{i\theta}
\nabla(\nabla\cdot A)
-(\nabla\cdot\nabla)A
\varepsilon_{ijk}\varepsilon_{k\ell m}\partial_j\partial_\ell A_m
= (\delta_{i\ell}\delta_{jm} - \delta_{im}\delta_{j\ell})\partial_j\partial_\ell A_m
= \partial_m\partial_i A_m - \partial_\ell\partial_\ell A_i
= \partial_i (\partial_m A_m) - (\partial_\ell\partial_\ell) A_i.
